Method Detail

replaceText

public void replaceText(CharSequence text)
We never allow ACTV to automatically replace the text, since we use "jamSuggestionQuery" to do that. There's no point in letting ACTV do this here, because in the search UI, as soon as we click a suggestion, we're going to start shutting things down.

Overrides:
replaceText in class AutoCompleteTextView
Parameters:
text - the selected suggestion in the drop down list

enoughToFilter

public boolean enoughToFilter()
We always return true, so that the effective threshold is "zero". This allows us to provide "null" suggestions such as "just show me some recent entries".

Overrides:
enoughToFilter in class AutoCompleteTextView
